        "verdict": "material",
        "reasoning": "The onboarding assumption was an enterprise software company. The strongest recent signal shows a major shift in treasury deployment: roughly $250M of corporate treasury moved into Bitcoin, about 60% of reserves. The surrounding coverage also consistently frames MicroStrategy/Strategy as a Bitcoin treasury proxy and digital asset treasury company, not primarily as an analytics software vendor. That does not mean the software business has disappeared, but it does indicate the company’s effective business model and risk profile have structurally drifted from low-risk enterprise software toward a BTC-linked treasury/holding model. This is material on the business_model axis."
